{"tid":1746031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[明報]【1122．理大】留守者阿翔收集物資：可在這裏守一個月 (20:12)","createTime":"2019-11-22T14:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T16:56:27.000Z","uid":20362,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"346c6c8011fc337a2de34b6da23ac7a192bf7591","tid":1746031,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:09:53.000Z","msg":"警方封鎖理大第六日，留守者行蹤隱秘，校園內可見到的人愈來愈少。連日來負責整理物資及清潔的阿翔（化名）表示，自己並無參與犯罪，無擲過汽油彈，不會應外來者「勸降」離開。他認為，校園環境衛生漸趨惡劣，「總要有人負責清理」。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者遇見阿翔時，他正在執拾散落一地的物資。他說，自己連日來負責洗廁所、清潔、收集乾糧等，慢慢把可用物資囤積起來，「預計可在這裏守一個月」，「度過這個冬天」。<br />\n<br />\n阿翔透露，現時雖然較少留守者出沒在校園範圍內，但他相信在校的仍有50至100多人，躲藏在各處。他亦有留意包圍理大的警察，評估過警力已減少三分之一，「門口的水炮車都駛走了」。圍堵在外的警察等待留守者出來，但他認為，警察終有一日亦會散去。<br />\n<br />\n密切留意警察行蹤，是否打算趁機逃走？阿翔說不是，他希望守着理大，又強調自己無犯法，不會「投降」出去，「清理又當參與罪行，煮嘢食又當參與罪行，急救又係參與罪行，我覺得好誇張囉」。本身不介意清潔的他，眼見校內衛生狀況愈見惡劣，亦希望出一分力。<br />\n<br />\n有別其他曾經留守理大的人，或受家人、教師、律師勸離，阿翔並無這方面的壓力。年約20歲的他，本來與家人關係疏離，靠打散工獨自生活，所以即使被困理大多日，他亦並無掛慮。不過，幾日前與他一起收集物資的同伴則選擇離開，「對我打擊都好大吓㗎，有成半日留喺張牀上面瞓」。但他明白，每人可負擔的並不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191122/s00001/1574424283707/%E3%80%901122-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%91%E7%95%99%E5%AE%88%E8%80%85%E9%98%BF%E7%BF%94%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E7%89%A9%E8%B3%87-%E5%8F%AF%E5%9C%A8%E9%80%99%E8%A3%8F%E5%AE%88%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191122%2Fs00001%2F1574424283707%2F%25E3%2580%25901122-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2598%25BF%25E7%25BF%2594%25E6%2594%25B6%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%2589%25A9%25E8%25B3%2587-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%2580%2599%25E8%25A3%258F%25E5%25AE%2588%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=f9678925\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191122%2Fs00001%2F1574424283707%2F%25E3%2580%25901122-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2598%25BF%25E7%25BF%2594%25E6%2594%25B6%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%2589%25A9%25E8%25B3%2587-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%2580%2599%25E8%25A3%258F%25E5%25AE%2588%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588&h=64e4f0c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191122/s00001/1574424283707/%E3%80%901122-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%91%E7%95%99%E5%AE%88%E8%80%85%E9%98%BF%E7%BF%94%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E7%89%A9%E8%B3%87-%E5%8F%AF%E5%9C%A8%E9%80%99%E8%A3%8F%E5%AE%88%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88</a>"},{"pid":"f229c64b0ad751b0c033546575d3230f5a3c820a","tid":1746031,"uid":20362,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:10:32.000Z","msg":"翔仔識玩<br />\n清理 整理物資係一定要做"},{"pid":"91bc46dd4f1c2ec1950fc6083ef176c438dbb50c","tid":1746031,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:14:46.000Z","msg":"多謝手足。需要什麼要同大家講。總有一日會贏"},{"pid":"4f47a2d0ff2f224ac26c9e1588214176ecf99d61","tid":1746031,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:25:30.000Z","msg":"仲要其實唔知翔仔有冇報細數/吹大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1454d76295e7787f20b5a332948eb17a13c5a5","tid":1746031,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:35:56.000Z","msg":"不過，幾日前與他一起收集物資的同伴則選擇離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a728750acb895a21bbf90bbadab38467cc8457e2","tid":1746031,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d1454d76295e7787f20b5a332948eb17a13c5a5","tid":1746031,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:35:56.000Z","msg":"不過，幾日前與他一起收集物資的同伴則選擇離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:06:35.000Z","msg":"可能全校得返佢一個係做清潔..."},{"pid":"f429f4d73c0730bf8cdb8125f28ff65df97a209f","tid":1746031,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:08:42.000Z","msg":"同伴離開 真係唔多唔少會有影響 因為大家並肩作戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4571ba8f2a595c2780dce027d317fa142a364842","tid":1746031,"uid":227637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a35e17dd5d0b56555d577c3327fefd57cfa7f2a5","tid":1746031,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:11:28.000Z","msg":"佢做得好好!<br />\n講真後生仔真係唔係人人都識做家務<br />\n加油~~"},{"pid":"a130168b5b0c9a223b491813546d892d2a3cec44","tid":1746031,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:12:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c57d7a993aa84f051b990de09885a8e223fc91b9","tid":1746031,"uid":210233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"阿翔靠你了,留在最後隨時無事"},{"pid":"0f5824831531e6c1cd136814401ce127d5f1679b","tid":1746031,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7450254d0490c8683cddcb88bc4249d766fc804","tid":1746031,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:18:54.000Z","msg":"其實可以點幫手足...... 除左一齊食生命麵包 星期日投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30caac2260eb0e17ad946b2e169e858b3d3f2e6","tid":1746031,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:21:36.000Z","msg":"住一世，解決土地問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油呀手足"},{"pid":"45383db03e8bd5c47fbda84d7237929dd5ca0bd6","tid":1746031,"uid":49546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:22:13.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n衛生問題真係要注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫人食廚師佬煮既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccedbde4e0df49df9757e6a279a8fe09c725468c","tid":1746031,"uid":160291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:24:57.000Z","msg":"佢係裹面上唔上到網架?"},{"pid":"42ff804517d69ce29fb355dd0a329f09c399f48c","tid":1746031,"uid":303805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:37:26.000Z","msg":"唔好用習慣既方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要大大力屌政府製造人道危機呀"},{"pid":"3347ea0de892657cea5c882ad2b92770567602aa","tid":1746031,"uid":293947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:25:28.000Z","msg":"應開始運用絕處求生術<br />\n1.趁斷水前,先要大量儲備食水以備不時之需<br />\n2.若斷電,認識後備發電機運作,用手頭物資做太陽爐,褒熱水過冬<br />\n3.可試種菜<br />\n4.若斷電,晚間燒垃圾取暖,可保校園清潔,防疫症爆發過冬季<br />\n5.現有肉類可用鹽保存<br />\n6.若有理科生發現太陽能設備要好好運用."},{"pid":"0d4cbd12d62df34ee797909a72cac0550e904b54","tid":1746031,"uid":61445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:43:09.000Z","msg":"小心安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51c6099ab4279888773d7dd35dd6e231d8254af","tid":1746031,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:44:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9df42f0184fb3b280164dff68820628f8e029ce1","tid":1746031,"uid":210233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:30:23.000Z","msg":"【圍困理大第七天】一名自稱「阿翔」的留守者，今天下午在會晤記者，表示自己當初只是「入嚟食個飯，清潔下」，然後就被困，很想「快啲出返去」。留守到第七天，他說精神方面的困擾比起身體狀況問題更大，「有一刻諗過自殺，只係一刻」。他坦言擔心其他留守者亦面對同樣問題，又透露校園估計還有約 50 人。<br />\n<br />\n***<br />\n<br />\n阿翔,我地支持你架。好想等你出來請你食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626bde16d2481fb605aa12a898e23e2410fbbb37","tid":1746031,"uid":51677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"見到佢地咁<br />\n好想佢地出來後請佢地食buffet <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食返餐好<br />\n理大手足加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14994eddd8d1a7e2c6ba7810775693b5d767b975","tid":1746031,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:56:09.000Z","msg":"11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8yQUK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8yQUK2.png&h=727d0b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誠邀：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、民主派議員、及候選人<br />\n<br />\n等候時及面對<span style=\"color: red;\">白警</span>時唱<strong>《Sing Hallelujah To The Lord》</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港區 6:00pm 灣仔紅隧入口集合，大量兩層巴士接過紅隧，或自行行過紅隧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">致 撞區候選人，<br />\n必在 11月 24日 7:30am 前，在facebook發表，證明已為<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7－11pm</span></strong>申請不反通知書，否則只有零票。</span></span><br />\n撞區表 <a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fcrashes%2F1&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=5abbadf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1</a><br />\n<br />\n下期預告：12.1 民主歌聲撐林夕 圍繞理大走一圈 【行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747254</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫幫手推一推行動post拉！連登重有邊個唔去投票！</span></span>"},{"pid":"cb44347f84fb5a6b3a1337ff16fe87ba6541aea5","tid":1746031,"uid":300649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"626bde16d2481fb605aa12a898e23e2410fbbb37","tid":1746031,"uid":51677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"見到佢地咁<br />\n好想佢地出來後請佢地食buffet <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食返餐好<br />\n理大手足加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:56:27.000Z","msg":"其實係咪可以宜家就請佢哋食返餐好嘢?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}